A woman died when a minibus taxi and a car collided while travelling along Vanilla Road on Tuesday morning. CAPE TOWN A woman has died and two others have been injured in an accident in Blue Downs. A minibus taxi and a car collided while travelling along Vanilla Road on Tuesday morning.ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring says: ER24 paramedics arrived on the scene and found the metro services already in attendance. Upon closer inspection, we found a woman lying on the pavement and two other men.&quot;We assessed the woman, believed to be in her 30s, and found that she has sustained numerous fatal injuries and showed no signs of life. (Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)